Package aspguidp.service.core.atom.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SimpleAtom
    Basic implementation of the Atom interface which allows the creation of an atom instance by a raw predicate name and a raw list of arguments.
    SimpleAtomHub
    Basic implementation of the AtomHub interface which uses array lists to store registered AtomSupplier instances and registered AtomConsumer instances.
